<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .container {
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ef7c00, #ff9933, #ef7c00);
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -moz-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            -moz-text-fill-color: transparent;
            line-height: 1;
        } 

        .error-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #d86e00;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .error-message {
            color: #995000;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ef7c00, #ff9933);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .home-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff9933, #ef7c00);
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .error-code {
                font-size: 6rem;
            }
            
            .error-title {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
        <h2 class="error-title">Page Not Found</h2>
        <p class="error-message">
            Oops! The page you're looking for seems to have wandered off into the digital wilderness. 
            Don't worry, you can always find your way back home using the button below.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="home-button">Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>